// Inline text style run management
// Provides a per-character style model on top of a compact run-length-encoded StyleRun array, supporting range queries, range mutations, toggle helpers for bold/italic/decoration, and run adjustment for insertions and deletions.
// synced: 2026-03-26T00:00:00Z

FUNCTION getStyleAt(runs, index) -> CharacterStyleOverride [2026-03-26]  EXPORT
  Finds the first run that contains the given character index and returns its style. Returns an empty object if no run covers that position.

---

FUNCTION expandRuns(runs, textLength) -> CharacterStyleOverride[] [2026-03-26]
  Expands the compact run array into a flat per-character style array of length textLength, merging overlapping runs.

---

FUNCTION applyStyleToRange(runs, start, end, patch, textLength) -> StyleRun[] [2026-03-26] EXPORT
  Expands runs to per-character styles, merges the patch object into characters [start, end), and recompacts into runs.

---

FUNCTION removeStyleFromRange(runs, start, end, keys, textLength) -> StyleRun[] [2026-03-26] EXPORT
  Expands runs, deletes the specified style keys from characters [start, end), and recompacts.

---

FUNCTION selectionHasStyle(runs, start, end, key, value) -> boolean [2026-03-26]  EXPORT
  CALLS: getStyleAt (style-runs)
  Returns true only if every character in [start, end) has the given style key equal to value.

---

FUNCTION compactRuns(chars) -> StyleRun[] [2026-03-26]
  Converts a flat per-character style array back into a minimal run-length-encoded StyleRun array, skipping null/empty slots and merging consecutive identical styles.

---

FUNCTION adjustRunsForInsert(runs, pos, insertLength) -> StyleRun[] [2026-03-26]  EXPORT
  Shifts run starts and expands run lengths to account for characters inserted at pos.

---

FUNCTION adjustRunsForDelete(runs, start, deleteLength) -> StyleRun[] [2026-03-26] EXPORT
  Removes or trims runs that fall within the deleted range and shifts remaining run starts backward.

---

FUNCTION toggleBoldInRange(runs, start, end, nodeWeight, textLength) -> { runs, newWeight } [2026-03-26] EXPORT
  CALLS: applyStyleToRange, removeStyleFromRange (style-runs)
  Checks if the entire selection is already bold; if so removes fontWeight, otherwise sets it to 700.

---

FUNCTION toggleItalicInRange(runs, start, end, nodeItalic, textLength) -> { runs, newItalic } [2026-03-26] EXPORT
  CALLS: applyStyleToRange, removeStyleFromRange (style-runs)
  Checks if the entire selection is already italic; toggles the italic property accordingly.

---

FUNCTION toggleDecorationInRange(runs, start, end, deco, nodeDeco, textLength) -> { runs, newDeco } [2026-03-26] EXPORT
  CALLS: applyStyleToRange, removeStyleFromRange (style-runs)
  Checks if every character in the selection already has the given text decoration; if so removes it, otherwise applies it.
